values: i am almost so happy that i will be leaving a certain someone behind... not because i want to get rid of him but because it hurts less to see him randomly then it does when he is just there right in front of your face and you cant do anything but look and long. i mean sure i would hit that again but damn we would make such a great couple! haha isnt that sad that i think about that kind of shit. i tried not to get all lame and sentimental in his yearbook... i was like "talk about making memories" haha we definitly did that! so i want him. bad. now. i need to face that i cant have him. " Keep quiet nothing cums as easy as you" hahah fall out boy says it all!! so i need to get a boyfriend... this shit is bananas! fuckin rediculous!

so i think i am more hurt than i lead on... i think it really bothers me for some reason that you know who is so torn up over some bitch.. i could treat him really good... too bad i prolly wont get the chance to be anything better than a fuck buddy *sigh*
